---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services">
  <section class="intro">
    <h1>Services</h1>
    <p class="long-form">
      The natural path of engagement begins with the individual leader. The CEO gains personal technical capability and structural clarity first, then brings this capacity to the rest of the organization.
    </p>
    <div class="rule"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>For Individuals</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Entry</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>~3hrs</span>
          <span>$1,500</span>
        </div>
        <p>A compressed formation experience. The threshold where capability begins to shift from AI-naive to AI-native.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Infrastructure</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>2 weeks</span>
          <span>$5,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Building tooling you control. Replacing rented platforms with self-determined infrastructure—tools, integrations, and workflows that persist.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Spar</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>Monthly</span>
          <span>$1,500 - $2,500</span>
        </div>
        <p>Ongoing formation with biweekly sessions and async access. Maintaining capability as the frontier moves and receiving structural counsel as situations evolve.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <h2>For Teams</h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Survey</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>$3,000 - $5,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Mapping current reality against desired outcomes. Establishing structural tension at the organizational level—seeing where things are and where they must go.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Construction</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>$8,000 - $15,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Building structures that persist. Implementing workflows, tools, and systems—built with the team so they understand what was built and can maintain it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Drill</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>$2,500 - $5,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Formation through repetition under pressure. Building team capacity until operation becomes automatic and oscillation back to old patterns is prevented.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="offering-card">
        <div class="structural-marker"></div>
        <h3>Continuity</h3>
        <div class="offering-meta">
          <span>Monthly</span>
          <span>$2,000 - $4,000</span>
        </div>
        <p>Sustained structural work. Maintaining team capability as tools and patterns advance, preventing the slide back to AI-naive operations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <h2>Initiate Contact</h2>
    <p class="long-form">
      Engagement begins with a direct conversation to assess structural fit.
    </p>
    <a href="/contact" class="production-link">Reach out</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
